1
00:00:01,396 --> 00:00:02,275
Thanks for the ride.

2
00:00:02,300 --> 00:00:03,000
Wait a minute.

3
00:00:03,733 --> 00:00:04,853
We need to talk.

4
00:00:05,360 --> 00:00:06,460
We can talk later.

5
00:00:07,100 --> 00:00:08,119
We can talk now.

6
00:00:08,900 --> 00:00:09,900
If you let me.

7
00:00:11,120 --> 00:00:12,400
What do we have to talk about?

8
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:12,900
Why now?

9
00:00:13,220 --> 00:00:15,160
Because we haven't talked at all for so
long.

10
00:00:15,280 --> 00:00:17,416
Your Aunt May and I don't even know who
you are anymore.

11
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:18,640
You shirk your chores.

12
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:22,380
You have all those weird experiments in
your room.

13
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:24,100
You start fights at school.

14
00:00:24,260 --> 00:00:25,380
I didn't start that fight.

15
00:00:25,460 --> 00:00:26,460
I told you that.

16
00:00:26,620 --> 00:00:27,840
You sure as hell finished.

17
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,560
What was I supposed to do?

18
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:29,980
Run away?

19
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:30,220
No.

20
00:00:30,380 --> 00:00:30,520
No.

21
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:31,900
You're not supposed to run away.

22
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:33,700
But... Pete, look.

23
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:34,920
You're changing.

24
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:35,440
I know.

25
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:37,800
I went through exactly the same thing at
your age.

26
00:00:37,980 --> 00:00:38,140
No.

27
00:00:38,340 --> 00:00:39,340
Not exactly.

28
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:40,800
Peter.

29
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:44,049
These are the years when
a man changes into the

30
00:00:44,050 --> 00:00:47,241
man he's going to
become the rest of his life.

31
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:50,400
Just be careful who you change into.

32
00:00:52,780 --> 00:00:54,580
This guy Flash Thompson.

33
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:57,180
He probably deserved what happened.

34
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:59,980
But just because you can beat him up...

35
00:01:01,199 --> 00:01:02,739
He doesn't give me the right to.

36
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:08,653
Remember... With great power... Comes
great responsibility.

37
00:01:09,540 --> 00:01:09,540
...comes great responsibility.

38
00:01:09,700 --> 00:01:12,540
Are you afraid that I'm going to turn into
some kind of criminal?

39
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,660
Quit worrying about me, okay?

40
00:01:15,140 --> 00:01:15,860
Something's different.

41
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:17,080
I'll figure it out.

42
00:01:17,380 --> 00:01:18,640
Stop lecturing me, please.

43
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:21,040
I don't mean to lecture and I don't mean
to preach.

44
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:23,240
And I know I'm not your father.

45
00:01:23,340 --> 00:01:24,640
Then stop pretending to be.

46
00:01:30,130 --> 00:01:31,130
Right.

47
00:01:34,350 --> 00:01:35,550
I'll pick you up here at 10.

